cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NA, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the relationship between two fundamental tools in machine learning and signal processing, namely the support vector machine (SVM) for classification and the Lasso technique used in regression. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses optimization algorithms and regularization paths, which are relevant to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
